buyOptions(uint256,address[],uint256[],a.details: Because tickers are one coin or the other depending on the price, one can only buy OTM options. You can get ITM put by buying OTM call and swapping, or get ITM call by buying OTM put and swapping. If you wanna swap, set sourceSwap to the asset you *dont* want, otherwise must be address(0x0)
buyOptions(uint256,address[],uint256[],a.notice: Buy a list of option. An option is a triplet [TRAddress, amount, putOrCall]

params.poolId: ID of the ROE lending pool
params.sourceSwap: Source swap address for call-put parity

close(uint256,address,address,uint256,ad.notice: Repays a TR debt and send tokens back to user

params.poolId: ID of the ROE lending pool
params.repayAmount: amount of borrowed tokens to repay; 0 or higher than current debt will repay all

executeOperation(address[],uint256[],uin.notice: Aave-compatible flashloan receiver dispatch: open a leverage position or liquidate a position

params.amounts: The amount of the flash-borrowed asset
params.assets: The address of the flash-borrowed asset
params.initiator: The address of the flashloan initiator
params.params: The byte-encoded params passed when initiating the flashloan
params.premiums: The fee of the flash-borrowed asset

returns.result: True if the execution of the operation succeeds, false otherwise

liquidate(uint256,address,address[],uint.details: Flashloan the debt tokens to liquidate, then use liquidation assets to repay the flashloan
liquidate(uint256,address,address[],uint.notice: Liquidate up to 50% of an unhealthy position

params.amounts: Array of borrowed Ticker assets amounts to repay
params.options: Array of borrowed Ticker assets to repay
params.poolId: ID of the ROE lending pool
params.user: The owner of the loan to liquidate

sellOptions(uint256,address,uint256,uint.details: Amounts aren't checked and will revert if wrong. In 99.9% cases one of the amounts should be 0Collateral needs to be in Lending Pool already

params.amount0: The amount of underlying token0 to add
params.amount1: The amount of underlying token1 to add
params.poolId: ID of the ROE lending pool

swapTokens(uint256,address,uint256).notice: Swap user assets; useful to change user risk profile

params.amount: of asset to swap - if 0, swap all
